# Engineering Guardrails

## Stack

- React + TypeScript
- Modern CSS + CSS variables
- Minimal dependencies

Code must be:
- readable
- predictable
- intentionally boring

---

## Do NOT Introduce

- Storybook
- token automation
- theming systems
- monorepos
- heavy abstractions
- experimental libraries

## Accessibility (Non-Negotiable)

- Keyboard accessible interactions
- Visible focus states
- WCAG AA contrast
- Motion respectful
